Not sure who all sees my posts anymore, but I just wanted to take a moment and thank the amazing crew at @blackvulturegallery and special thanks to my friend @hoode215 for taking me in for the past 3 years. Y’all were my family when I had none, and I’m excited to come back for periodic visits in the future! (If you have a May appt - don’t worry, I’ll be back!)

For now, I’m headed to Hawaii to build/homestead on my land - very exciting things in the works!

I’ll keep y’all posted. Huge thanks to anyone who still follows me, and my loyal clients for your love and support! 🖤🖤🖤

Headin outta Philly (for now) and 2023 with a boom! One of my favorite pieces of the year - thanks @hammer.hands for your commitment to this mostly freehand project - you killed it! Parts healed, parts fresh. 🖤🖤🖤
